                "text": "Let's solve the equation:\n\n\\[\n\\sin(x) + x^2 = 42\n\\]\n\nThis is a transcendental equation (it involves both a trigonometric and an algebraic term), so it cannot be solved exactly using algebraic methods. We will need to use numerical methods to find the solution(s).\n\nI'll solve it now.",
