            "code": "import numpy as np\nfrom scipy.optimize import fsolve\n\n# Define the equation\ndef equation(x):\n    return np.sin(x) + x**2 - 42\n\n# Provide an initial guess\n# Since x^2 dominates for large x, let's try positive and negative values\n\ninitial_guesses = [6, -6]\n\nsolutions = [fsolve(equation, guess)[0] for guess in initial_guesses]\n\nsolutions",
